66
00:03:36,371 --> 00:03:38,839
A tool like this seems very promising,

67
00:03:38,839 --> 00:03:42,946
and it is probably the very first 
type of analysis that one could do

68
00:03:42,946 --> 00:03:45,273
when one's called 
