114
00:05:59,790 --> 00:06:03,391
This is the case for 
a fully immersed slope underwater.

115
00:06:03,391 --> 00:06:05,301
If the water is moving inside the slope,

116
00:06:05,301 --> 00:06:07,708
in the particular case 
in which we have flow lines

117
00:06:07,708 --> 00:06:09,527
which are parallel to the slope,

118
00:06:09,527 --> 00:06:13,142
this is the final formula that we get
